Johannesburg- Durban-based businesswoman Shauwn Mkhize recently treated herself to a trip under the sun in Namibia. Mkhize went on a much-needed trip of chasing the sun in the beautiful deserts of Namibia. The flamboyant owner of the PSL side, Royal AM, made sure that she captured her entire trip and made some beautiful memories whilst she was away on her vacation. “It’s true what they say, a journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step. Yesterday, I woke up in the comfort of my bed in SA, and today I’m in a foreign land with a beauty that is truly unmatched,” she wrote.          For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.